text: The Emigrant (, translit. Al Mohager) is a 1994 Egyptian French drama movie directed by Youssef Chahine and starring Hanan Tork, Khaled El Nabawy, Mahmoud Hemida, Yousra, Safia El Emari. ==Other websites== * Category:1994 drama movies Category:Egyptian movies Category:French drama movies Category:Movies directed by Youssef Chahine
